OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain
OL,6,Fspreading east to all areas through
OL,7,FThursday evening, becoming persistent
OL,8,Fovernight into Friday, with some
OL,9,Fheavier bursts probable. Turning
OL,10,Fcolder with an increasing risk of
OL,11,Fsleet or snow over higher ground,
OL,12,Fmainly Cheviots and Pennines.
OL,13,
OL,14,CFriday:FRain gradually easing into
OL,15,FFriday with cloud eventually breaking
OL,16,Fto perhaps giving some late
OL,17,Fbrightness. Feeling cold by day under
OL,18,Fwidespread cloud, and a cold night
OL,19,Finto Saturday with frost.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
