OL,3,GNorth East
OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Saturday to Monday:FA
OL,6,Fdrier and brighter day likely Saturday
OL,7,Fafter a cold start. Likely turning
OL,8,Fcloudier and milder into Sunday and
OL,9,FMonday, with low cloud, fog and some
OL,10,Frain returning.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
